Version 0.9.0
=============

:Released: 2016-06-10
:Maintainer: Jens Luetkens <j.luetkens@limitland.de>

* Move the original repository to gitlab.com
* Increase the shadows transparency.


Version 0.8.2
=============

:Released: 2013-10-23
:Maintainer: Jens Luetkens <j.luetkens@limitland.de>

* Correct build of entire cursor set from source.
* Explain how to set cursor size in Gnome 3.
* Correct transparency level for Opaque cursors.
* Set hairline colour consistently.


Version 0.8.1
=============

:Released: 2013-10-12
:Maintainer: Jens Luetkens <j.luetkens@limitland.de>

* Set orientation RightHanded if not specified.
* Build theme variants.
* Fix the multisize build process from sources.


Version 0.8
===========

:Released: 2013-09-21
:Maintainer: Jens Luetkens <j.luetkens@limitland.de>

* Use multisize cursors.


Version 0.7.4
=============

:Released: 2012-08-13
:Maintainer: Jens Luetkens <j.luetkens@limitland.de>

* Switch from deprecated ‘rsvg(1)’ to ‘rsvg-convert(1)’.


Version 0.7.3
=============

:Released: 2011-09-13
:Maintainer: Jens Luetkens <j.luetkens@limitland.de>

* Updated documentation for building custom themes.

* Expand shell wildcards in rule dependencies.


Version 0.7.2
=============

:Released: 2011-02-26
:Maintainer: Jens Luetkens <j.luetkens@limitland.de>

* Added all missing cursor links from Qt4 documentation.


Version 0.7.1
=============

:Released: 2010-10-16
:Maintainer: Jens Luetkens <j.luetkens@limitland.de>

* Added Qt4 cursor links


Version 0.7
===========

:Released: 2010-06-03
:Maintainer: Jens Luetkens <j.luetkens@limitland.de>

* Licence changed to GPLv3.

* Uninstallation of current/custom/all cursors from sources.

* Render images using ‘rsvg’ (faster than Inkscape).

* Generate animation frames from starting image using SVG transform
  attributes (not ‘patch’).

* Easier to customise install location.

* Maintainability improvements of build system and programs.

* Include “Opaque” and “Left Handed” alternatives in primary source
  package.


Version 0.6.1
=============

:Released: 2009-11-02
:Maintainer: Jens Luetkens <j.luetkens@limitland.de>

* Fix install script to process all files correctly.


Version 0.6.0
=============

:Released: 2009-06-19
:Maintainer: Jens Luetkens <j.luetkens@endiancode.de>

* License changed to LGPLv3.

* Added red cursors.

* Fix some firefox cursor hashes (thanx to tks).


Version 0.5.1
=============

:Released: 2008-05-28
:Maintainer: Jens Luetkens <j.luetkens@endiancode.de>

* Progress animation expanded to 24 frames.

* Wait cursor fixes.

* Zoom cursor fixes.


Version 0.5.0
=============

:Released: 2007-09-14
:Maintainer: Jens Luetkens <j.luetkens@limitland.de>

* Optimized build script caching shadow files.

* SVGs and HOTSPOTS scaled to 500x500 to match svg2png script.

* Slight svg fixes and cleanup.

* Opaque versions.


